# Lessons

Past corrections and patterns to remember. Updated after every mistake.

## How to add a lesson
After any correction during a session, log it here:
```
## [short description]
**Wrong:** what was generated incorrectly
**Right:** what the correct pattern is
**Why:** why the correct pattern matters
```

